WEBVTT

00:05.373 --> 00:07.375
male announcer:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:07.408 --> 00:11.279
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:11.312 --> 00:13.514
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:13.547 --> 00:15.483
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:15.516 --> 00:16.817
ARE MEMBERS OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:16.850 --> 00:19.120
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:19.153 --> 00:21.155
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:22.290 --> 00:24.792
- AMBER, WHERE THE HELL
ARE YOU?

00:24.825 --> 00:28.796
- GOOD THING
I LIKE SLOWPOKES.

00:28.829 --> 00:31.265
- [panting]

00:31.299 --> 00:38.406
- [laughs]

00:38.439 --> 00:42.543
- HEY.

00:42.576 --> 00:44.478
YOU SEEING ANYTHING?

00:44.512 --> 00:47.381
- NO, IT'S LATE,
THE MOTHERS ARE GOING IN,

00:47.415 --> 00:49.350
I DON'T THINK
OUR GUY'S GONNA SHOW.

00:49.383 --> 00:52.820
- NO, HE GROPED TEN WOMEN
IN THE LAST SIX WEEKS.

00:52.853 --> 00:54.822
DO YOU THINK
HE'S JUST GONNA STOP NOW?

00:54.855 --> 00:55.823
- IT'S GETTING COLDER.

00:55.856 --> 00:57.825
IT'S HARD TO COP A FEEL
THROUGH A HEAVY COAT.

00:57.858 --> 00:59.160
MAYBE HE GOES SOUTH
FOR THE WINTER.

00:59.193 --> 01:00.394
- OH, COME ON.

01:00.428 --> 01:02.863
- HEY!
WHERE'D YOU GO?

01:02.896 --> 01:06.467
WHERE ARE YOU?
[laughs]

01:06.500 --> 01:08.336
[grunting and panting]

01:08.369 --> 01:10.571
- IS THAT OUR GUY?

01:10.604 --> 01:13.141
- WHOEVER IT IS,
HE'S NOT RIGHT.

01:13.174 --> 01:16.510
- NOT READY?
AMBER!

01:16.544 --> 01:19.180
IT'S A JACKHAMMER!
[laughs]

01:19.213 --> 01:21.182
- HEY, WHAT THE HELL
IS YOUR PROBLEM?

01:21.215 --> 01:22.150
[overlapping shouts]

01:22.183 --> 01:23.417
- EVERYBODY, BACK UP.
BACK UP, BACK UP. SIR!

01:23.451 --> 01:26.187
POLICE.
DON'T EVEN THINK ABOUT IT.

01:26.220 --> 01:28.589
PUT IT DOWN. BACK UP. LET'S GET
SOME ROOM HERE. BACK UP.

01:28.622 --> 01:30.524
- ROLLINS.

01:30.558 --> 01:32.560
- OH, GOD.

01:32.593 --> 01:34.228
HEY, SIR.
HEY.

01:34.262 --> 01:36.864
- [laughing]

01:36.897 --> 01:38.199
- IT'S NOT FUNNY.

01:38.232 --> 01:41.602
YOU'RE SUCH
A BITCH.

01:41.635 --> 01:43.837
- WHO THE HELL
YOU TALKING TO?

01:43.871 --> 01:45.473
- MY GIRLFRIEND,
AMBER.

01:45.506 --> 01:49.177
SHE'S RIGHT THERE.
MAKE HER STOP.

01:49.210 --> 01:50.844
- HE'S HALLUCINATING.
HE'S BURNING UP.

01:50.878 --> 01:52.846
- SVU PORTABLE
TO CENTRAL K.

01:52.880 --> 01:55.383
WE GOT A 54
IN THE MEER.

01:55.416 --> 01:59.220
WE NEED A BUS FOR TRANSPORTATION
TO LAGUARDIA PSYCHIATRIC ASAP.

01:59.253 --> 02:02.156
- THE PSYCH E.R.?

02:02.190 --> 02:03.757
UGH,
WHAT FOR?

02:03.791 --> 02:06.394
- HE HAS TO BE CLEARED BY
A SHRINK BEFORE WE CAN BOOK HIM.

02:06.427 --> 02:07.495
- THE GUY IS NOT NUTS.

02:07.528 --> 02:09.363
HE'S HAVING A BAD TRIP.
THAT'S IT.

02:09.397 --> 02:11.265
- COME ON,
YOU CAN TELL THE DIFFERENCE

02:11.299 --> 02:13.501
BETWEEN A CHEMICAL WIG-OUT
AND A PSYCHOTIC BREAK?

02:13.534 --> 02:14.902
- YEAH, I CAN.

02:14.935 --> 02:18.172
MOST OF THE TIME.

02:22.343 --> 02:26.247
I GREW UP
AROUND BOTH.

02:26.280 --> 02:28.416
MY SISTER
HAD IT ROUGH, SO...

02:28.449 --> 02:30.951
- WE ALL COME
FROM SOMETHING.

02:30.984 --> 02:32.853
- [chuckles]
- THIS WON'T TAKE LONG.

02:32.886 --> 02:35.456
COME ON.

02:35.489 --> 02:37.258
CAPTAIN LEE.

02:37.291 --> 02:38.526
- WHAT'S HAPPENING?

02:38.559 --> 02:39.860
- DETECTIVE ROLLINS.
- HEY, HOW YA DOIN'?

02:39.893 --> 02:41.028
- ALL RIGHT.

02:41.061 --> 02:43.897
I JUST WATCHED YOU TWO PINCH
THE NAKED FISH ON YOUTUBE.

02:43.931 --> 02:45.933
2,000 HITS.

02:45.966 --> 02:47.868
- READY?

02:47.901 --> 02:49.937
- [groaning]

02:49.970 --> 02:51.071
- ANY IDEA
WHAT HE TOOK?

02:51.104 --> 02:53.574
- YEAH, HE WAS RUNNING AROUND
WITHOUT ANY CLOTHES ON.

02:53.607 --> 02:55.443
COLLAPSING,
NO TREMORS.

02:55.476 --> 02:56.577
IT COULD BE P.C.P.

02:56.610 --> 02:58.579
- PROBABLY.

02:58.612 --> 03:00.848
WE'LL RUN A TOX SCREEN
AND SEE WHAT HAPPENS.

03:00.881 --> 03:02.516
RUN AN E.K.G. AND A CAT
ONCE HE'S STABLE.

03:02.550 --> 03:03.817
- HE'S ALL YOURS?

03:03.851 --> 03:05.553
- FOR NOW.

03:05.586 --> 03:07.221
- NO NEED
TO BABYSIT.

03:07.255 --> 03:09.323
WHY DON'T Y'ALL GO HOME?
I GOT THIS.

03:09.357 --> 03:11.459
- SURE?
- YEAH.

03:11.492 --> 03:16.330
- GUESS WE'LL SEE HIM
AT ARRAIGNMENT.

03:18.499 --> 03:21.269
- [groans]

03:21.302 --> 03:23.003
I'M SICK.

03:23.036 --> 03:25.339
PLEASE,
I NEED A DOCTOR.

03:25.373 --> 03:26.274
- SOON AS YOU GET
YOUR E.K.G.,

03:26.307 --> 03:27.808
YOU'RE GOING STRAIGHT TO JAIL.
NOW SHUT UP.

03:27.841 --> 03:29.310
- 10-85.
PATIENT EJECT.

03:29.343 --> 03:31.479
WARD SIX.
NEED ASSISTANCE.

03:31.512 --> 03:32.513
[alarm going off]

03:32.546 --> 03:35.383
- STAY HERE.
YOU MOVE, I POUND YOU.

03:35.416 --> 03:37.318
- GET AWAY FROM ME!

03:37.351 --> 03:40.354
[screaming and commotion]

03:50.364 --> 03:56.370
- [whimpering]

04:00.574 --> 04:03.311
[groaning]

04:12.953 --> 04:14.054
[yelling]

04:14.087 --> 04:16.290
- GET LOST.

04:16.324 --> 04:17.858
SHUT THE DOOR.

04:17.891 --> 04:23.331
SHUT THE DOOR!

04:25.633 --> 04:27.801
- SOMEBODY!

04:27.835 --> 04:29.069
HEY!

04:29.102 --> 04:31.372
HEY, HELP!

04:31.405 --> 04:35.042
RAPE!
RAPE!

04:35.075 --> 04:38.045
[dramatic music]

04:38.078 --> 04:44.284
*

05:23.023 --> 05:24.625
- NEXT CASE?

05:24.658 --> 05:26.927
- PEOPLE VERSUS
DARREN BICKFORD.

05:26.960 --> 05:29.997
ONE COUNT EXPOSURE,
ONE COUNT PUBLIC LEWDNESS.

05:30.030 --> 05:31.064
- HOW DO YOU PLEAD?

05:31.098 --> 05:32.966
- I SAW A GIRL
GET RAPED LAST NIGHT.

05:33.000 --> 05:35.135
- NOT TODAY. COUNSELOR--
- LISTEN TO ME.

05:35.168 --> 05:37.971
A GIRL WAS ATTACKED.

05:38.005 --> 05:39.407
I KNOW WHAT I SAW.

05:39.440 --> 05:40.841
I'M NOT
MAKING THIS UP.

05:40.874 --> 05:43.444
A GUY
WAS CHOKING HER.

05:43.477 --> 05:46.547
I TOLD THE DOCTORS,
TH-THE GUARDS,

05:46.580 --> 05:50.651
NOW I'M TELLING YOU.

05:50.684 --> 05:52.386
- ARE YOU
THE ARRESTING OFFICERS?

05:52.420 --> 05:53.887
- YES, MANHATTAN SVU,
YOUR HONOR.

05:53.921 --> 05:57.991
AND THIS IS THE FIRST TIME WE'VE
HEARD ANYTHING ABOUT A RAPE.

05:58.025 --> 06:00.461
- GOOD, THEN YOU
CAN INVESTIGATE STARTING NOW.

06:00.494 --> 06:03.597
- WITH ALL DUE RESPECT,
MA'AM,

06:03.631 --> 06:06.434
THE SUSPECT WAS APPREHENDED
WHILE MASTURBATING PUBLICLY

06:06.467 --> 06:08.068
UNDER A DRUG-INDUCED
HALLUCINATION.

06:08.101 --> 06:11.439
- WAS HE SEEING THINGS
WHEN HE WITNESSED THE RAPE?

06:11.472 --> 06:15.909
- I WOULD HAVE NO WAY
OF KNOWING, YOUR HONOR.

06:15.943 --> 06:17.545
- THEN DON'T SPECULATE.

06:17.578 --> 06:20.147
WE'LL RECONVENE
IN TWO WEEKS.

06:20.180 --> 06:22.049
I EXPECT TO HEAR
FROM THE PEOPLE

06:22.082 --> 06:25.385
ABOUT THE DEFENDANT'S COMPLAINT
AT THAT TIME.

06:29.957 --> 06:32.192
- A GIRL GOT RAPED.

06:32.225 --> 06:33.461
I SWEAR
I'M TELLING THE TRUTH.

06:33.494 --> 06:35.429
- WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
IT WAS A RAPE?

06:35.463 --> 06:38.031
- SHE WAS ON TOP OF HIM,
FACING ME--

06:38.065 --> 06:40.000
- SHE WAS ON TOP?
- YEAH.

06:40.033 --> 06:44.137
BUT HIS ARM WAS AROUND HER NECK,
CHOKING HER.

06:44.171 --> 06:45.138
HER EYES
WERE SHUT TIGHT.

06:45.172 --> 06:47.174
SHE WAS CRYING.

06:47.207 --> 06:48.208
- WHAT DID SHE
LOOK LIKE?

06:48.241 --> 06:53.447
- WHITE GIRL,
DARK BLONDE HAIR.

06:53.481 --> 06:55.048
YOUNG.
I-I DON'T KNOW.

06:55.082 --> 06:56.183
- WHAT ABOUT
THE DOER?

06:56.216 --> 06:57.184
YOU SEE HIS FACE?

06:57.217 --> 06:58.652
- NO,
SHE WAS BLOCKING HIM.

06:58.686 --> 07:00.921
HE YELLED, "GET LOST,
SHUT THE DOOR!"

07:00.954 --> 07:02.556
- DID ANYBODY ELSE
SEE THIS?

07:02.590 --> 07:03.557
LIKE, MAYBE A GUARD?

07:03.591 --> 07:05.926
- I WAS, UH,
ON MY OWN.

07:05.959 --> 07:09.229
LOOK, SHE WAS TRYING TO PULL
HIS ARM FROM HER NECK, AND...

07:09.262 --> 07:12.833
SHE HAD A HOSPITAL BRACELET
AND A-A-A--

07:12.866 --> 07:15.035
A DEEP SCAR ON THE INSIDE
OF HER LEFT ARM.

07:15.068 --> 07:17.538
SHE TRIED TO
KILLED HERSELF.

07:17.571 --> 07:20.040
- THERE'S PLENTY OF SUICIDE
ATTEMPTS IN A PSYCH WARD.

07:20.073 --> 07:22.610
- GO BACK TO LAGUARDIA,
WARD SIX.

07:22.643 --> 07:25.145
SHE'S REAL.

07:25.178 --> 07:27.481
[knock at door]

07:27.515 --> 07:30.518
- KEEP YOUR CLOTHES ON.

07:33.721 --> 07:35.889
- SO WE HAVE A FLASHER
WHO WAS HALLUCINATING,

07:35.923 --> 07:38.258
CLAIMS TO HAVE SEEN A GIRL
RAPED AT LAGUARDIA.

07:38.291 --> 07:40.160
CAN'T WE FARM THIS ONE OUT?
- NOT ACCORDING TO THE JUDGE.

07:40.193 --> 07:41.294
- THIS KID WAS
HIGH AS A KITE.

07:41.328 --> 07:44.498
WHO SAYS HE SAW ANYTHING AT ALL?
- THE RAPE WAS, WHAT?

07:44.532 --> 07:47.067
FIVE HOURS AFTER YOU BUSTED HIM?
HE WOULD HAVE COME DOWN BY THEN.

07:47.100 --> 07:48.268
- IF THERE WAS A RAPE,
YEAH.

07:48.301 --> 07:49.670
- WHY WOULD HE LIE?

07:49.703 --> 07:51.872
PUBLIC LEWDNESS,
FIRST OFFENSE...

07:51.905 --> 07:54.975
WHAT'S HE LOOKING AT,
A WEEK OF COMMUNITY SERVICE?

07:55.008 --> 07:56.510
- I DON'T THINK THIS GUY
PREMEDITATES OR EVEN THINKS.

07:56.544 --> 07:58.879
WE HAVE A DESCRIPTION,
WE GO TO LAGUARDIA.

07:58.912 --> 08:02.950
IF THE GIRL EXISTS,
WE FIND HER.

08:04.184 --> 08:04.985
- WE NEED
TO TALK TO YOU

08:05.018 --> 08:07.254
ABOUT ONE OF YOUR
FEMALE PATIENTS.

08:07.287 --> 08:09.122
- WHICH ONE?
- WELL, WE DON'T HAVE A NAME.

08:09.156 --> 08:13.093
BUT SHE'S WHITE, SHE'S MID-20s,
DARK BLONDE HAIR.

08:13.126 --> 08:15.529
SHE'S GOT VERTICAL SCARS
ON HER FOREARM.

08:15.563 --> 08:18.198
- THAT'S GIA ESKAS.
OH, MY GOD.

08:18.231 --> 08:20.033
- WHAT'S SHE
BEING TREATED FOR?

08:20.067 --> 08:21.234
- SORRY, YOU KNOW
I CAN'T ANSWER THAT.

08:21.268 --> 08:22.369
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT?

08:22.402 --> 08:24.872
- WELL, WE THINK SHE MAY
HAVE BEEN RAPED LAST NIGHT.

08:24.905 --> 08:27.240
- WHAT? BY WHO?

08:27.274 --> 08:28.275
- WE DON'T KNOW.

08:28.308 --> 08:30.210
THAT'S WHY WE NEED
TO TALK TO HER.

08:30.243 --> 08:31.278
YOU DIDN'T GET
A REPORT?

08:31.311 --> 08:33.180
- NO.

08:33.213 --> 08:36.283
BUT SHE HAD TO BE SEDATED
LAST NIGHT.

08:36.316 --> 08:38.285
- WHY?

08:38.318 --> 08:41.288
IS SHE LUCID NOW?
- SHE SHOULD BE.

08:41.321 --> 08:42.623
I'LL GO IN WITH YOU.
- I'M SORRY, DOC.

08:42.656 --> 08:44.958
IT'S A CRIMINAL
INVESTIGATION.

08:48.061 --> 08:52.099
- I GOT A HAIR.

08:52.132 --> 08:54.167
THE COLOR MATCHES
OUR SUPPOSED VICTIM.

08:54.201 --> 08:56.036
- YOU SHOULD FIND PLENTY.

08:56.069 --> 08:57.337
DOCS CRASH OUT HERE
ALL THE TIME

08:57.370 --> 08:59.873
WHEN THEY GOT PATIENTS
ON THE WARD.

08:59.907 --> 09:01.174
- SLEEP'S NOT THE ONLY THING
GOING ON HERE.

09:01.208 --> 09:03.276
CUSHION'S COVERED
IN STAINS.

09:03.310 --> 09:04.878
- A QUICKIE WITH A NURSE
ISN'T RAPE.

09:04.912 --> 09:06.079
MAYBE THAT'S WHAT WENT DOWN.
- HOW WOULD YOU KNOW?

09:06.113 --> 09:08.348
YOU LEFT YOUR PRISONER
UNATTENDED.

09:08.381 --> 09:11.919
- HE WAS HANDCUFFED TO
A WHEELCHAIR ON A LOCKED WARD.

09:11.952 --> 09:14.888
- LOOK, I DID VERTICAL PATROLS
IN HOUSING PROJECTS

09:14.922 --> 09:16.657
FOR SIX YEARS,
I GET IT.

09:16.690 --> 09:18.692
THEY EXPECT YOU TO HAVE EYES
IN THE BACK OF YOUR HEAD.

09:18.726 --> 09:22.062
- 85 CALL WENT DOWN.

09:22.095 --> 09:23.931
PATIENT GOING BUCK WILD
IN WARD SIX.

09:23.964 --> 09:26.166
ATTACKED AN OFFICER
AND TWO NURSES, ALL HANDS.

09:26.199 --> 09:28.936
- HOW MANY SURVEILLANCE CAMERAS
ARE THERE ON THIS FLOOR?

09:28.969 --> 09:30.203
- THERE'S TWO
AT THE VISITORS' DESK.

09:30.237 --> 09:35.876
LET ME, UH,
GET YOU THE FOOTAGE.

09:35.909 --> 09:38.111
- WHO TOLD YOU THAT?

09:38.145 --> 09:39.279
IF IT WAS ONE
OF MY FELLOW INMATES,

09:39.312 --> 09:40.347
YOU CAN'T BELIEVE
A WORD THEY SAY.

09:40.380 --> 09:41.949
THEY'RE ALL CRAZY.

09:41.982 --> 09:45.653
- IS THAT A YES
OR A NO?

09:45.686 --> 09:48.088
- GIA?

09:48.121 --> 09:49.890
WILL YOU PLEASE
TELL US?

09:49.923 --> 09:52.626
DID SOMETHING HAPPEN LAST NIGHT?
- THERE YOU ARE.

09:52.660 --> 09:56.263
MOMMY JUST BROUGHT ME SOME
CIGGIES, LET'S--

09:56.296 --> 09:57.264
BAD TIME?

09:57.297 --> 09:58.866
- NO,
NOT AT ALL.

09:58.899 --> 10:00.067
CAGNEY AND LACEY
WERE JUST LEAVING.

10:00.100 --> 10:01.001
- ACTUALLY,
GIA...

10:01.034 --> 10:02.402
IF WE COULD HAVE
ANOTHER MINUTE WITH YOU,

10:02.435 --> 10:04.271
WE WOULD APPRECIATE IT.

10:04.304 --> 10:08.408
SO, GIA, WE HEARD THAT YOU WERE
REALLY, REALLY UPSET LAST NIGHT.

10:08.441 --> 10:11.879
TO THE POINT WHERE
YOU HAD TO BE SEDATED.

10:11.912 --> 10:13.280
WHY WAS THAT?

10:13.313 --> 10:16.249
- UH,
BAD HAIR DAY.

10:16.283 --> 10:17.718
- MAYBE IT WAS
A LITTLE MORE THAN THAT?

10:17.751 --> 10:19.019
- WHO KNOWS?

10:19.052 --> 10:22.122
UH, I'M WORKING
ON FINDING MY TRIGGERS.

10:22.155 --> 10:25.325
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.

10:25.358 --> 10:27.661
I WAS MAKING
A NOOSE.

10:27.695 --> 10:30.297
THEY CAUGHT ME
RIPPING MY SHEETS.

10:30.330 --> 10:34.167
LAST TIME,
I USED A RAZOR.

10:34.201 --> 10:36.970
I'M A FREQUENT FLIER, YOU'D
THINK I'D GET IT RIGHT BY NOW.

10:37.004 --> 10:39.072
- SO THIS ISN'T THE FIRST TIME
YOU'VE BEEN HERE?

10:39.106 --> 10:41.274
- SOME GIRLS TRAVEL
OR GO TO COLLEGE TO GET AWAY.

10:41.308 --> 10:43.911
ME, I VACATION
AT LAGUARDIA PSYCHIATRIC.

10:43.944 --> 10:48.716
- LET'S GO BACK
TO LAST NIGHT.

10:48.749 --> 10:49.883
YOU RECOGNIZE THIS GUY?

10:49.917 --> 10:52.452
- YOU KNOW, UH,
THEY UPPED MY MEDS.

10:52.485 --> 10:54.021
SO EVERYTHING'S
A BIT FUZZY.

10:54.054 --> 10:56.089
- HE SAID HE SAW YOU
GET RAPED.

10:56.123 --> 10:59.026
- YEAH, WELL, I THINK
I'D REMEMBER IF I'D BEEN RAPED.

10:59.059 --> 11:01.461
- GIA, IF YOU'RE WORRIED OR
AFRAID, WE CAN PROTECT YOU.

11:01.494 --> 11:04.164
- FROM WHO?
MYSELF?

11:04.197 --> 11:06.099
- GIA...

11:06.133 --> 11:09.669
THE BEST WAY TO MAKE THIS
GO AWAY IS WITH A RAPE KIT.

11:16.143 --> 11:17.110
- A RAPE KIT?

11:17.144 --> 11:19.179
- YEAH.

11:19.212 --> 11:22.015
- WHAT HAPPENS
IF YOU FIND SOMETHING?

11:22.049 --> 11:27.120
- WILL WE?

11:27.154 --> 11:29.389
- SO IF I DO IT,
WILL YOU LET ME, UH...

11:29.422 --> 11:34.895
WILL YOU LEAVE ME
ALONE?

11:34.928 --> 11:37.130
- SHE WANTS US
TO DO THE RAPE KIT.

11:37.164 --> 11:39.399
SHE KNOWS
WE'LL FIND PROOF.

11:39.432 --> 11:42.035
- OF WHAT?
SEX?

11:42.069 --> 11:44.237
PATIENTS GET IT ON
WITH EACH OTHER ALL THE TIME.

11:44.271 --> 11:47.074
- SHE SHOWS CLASSIC SIGNS
OF ASSAULT.

11:47.107 --> 11:49.076
HYPERVIGILANCE,
FEAR, DENIAL--

11:49.109 --> 11:51.378
- ALL OF WHICH COULD BE SYMPTOMS
OF HER MENTAL ILLNESS.

11:51.411 --> 11:53.313
- WELL, GIA THINKS THAT
NOBODY WILL BELIEVE HER.

11:53.346 --> 11:55.082
I THINK SHE'S RIGHT.

11:55.115 --> 11:56.416
- NO, I'M NOT SAYING
SHE'S A LIAR.

11:56.449 --> 11:58.385
