TO GET ANYBODY TO BELIEVE HER.

12:10.097 --> 12:13.100
- WHICH MAKES HER
THE PERFECT TARGET.

12:20.407 --> 12:21.975
- SHE TOLD YOU
SHE WASN'T ATTACKED?

12:22.009 --> 12:23.376
DO YOU BELIEVE HER
OR YOUR WITNESS?

12:23.410 --> 12:25.145
- WELL, SHE DID AGREE
TO A RAPE KIT.

12:25.178 --> 12:27.948
I THINK THAT SHE WANTS US
TO FIND SOMETHING

12:27.981 --> 12:29.983
WITHOUT HAVING
TO ADMIT IT.

12:30.017 --> 12:32.319
- I UNDERSTAND DENIAL,
DETECTIVE.

12:32.352 --> 12:34.988
AND OBVIOUSLY,
IF SOMETHING DID HAPPEN TO HER,

12:35.022 --> 12:36.356
I WANT TO KNOW.

12:36.389 --> 12:39.326
- ALL RIGHT, GIA'S HOUSED
IN A LOCKED WARD, RIGHT?

12:39.359 --> 12:40.393
WHO HAS ACCESS?

12:40.427 --> 12:42.963
- EMPLOYEES,
OTHER PATIENTS.

12:42.996 --> 12:44.932
- ANY ISSUES
WITH THE STAFF?

12:44.965 --> 12:46.399
- OUR PATIENT POPULATION
IS VULNERABLE,

12:46.433 --> 12:49.402
SO EVERY HIRE IS VETTED, AND
THERE HAVE BEEN NO ACCUSATIONS.

12:49.436 --> 12:50.904
