- YOU KNOW WHAT? THAT'S PROBABLY
EXACTLY WHAT GIA SAID

29:05.144 --> 29:08.147
TO YOUR HUSBAND THE FIRST TIME
HE RAPED HER.

29:16.255 --> 29:20.326
- GIA WAS A SWEET GIRL
IN A BAD SITUATION.

29:20.359 --> 29:23.395
HER FATHER
WAS FALLING APART.

29:23.429 --> 29:26.532
