THAT I'M A CLICHE?

29:40.212 --> 29:41.413
A MIDDLE-AGED,
MARRIED MAN IN LOVE

29:41.447 --> 29:44.283
WITH A GIRL
HALF MY AGE.

29:44.316 --> 29:48.387
WHAT WE HAVE IS REAL.

29:48.420 --> 29:52.158
- YEAH,
I GET THAT.

29:52.191 --> 29:57.329
