ABOUT HER PINK BRA.

34:10.282 --> 34:12.351
HE SAYS
THEY'RE IN LOVE.

34:12.384 --> 34:15.154
- OKAY, I WON'T EVEN
LISTEN TO THIS.

34:15.187 --> 34:16.155
