HE CAME PRETTY CLOSE.

35:31.297 --> 35:33.165
- HOW DO YOU HANDLE IT?

35:36.268 --> 35:37.836
- YOU DO
EVERYTHING YOU CAN

35:37.869 --> 35:40.872
