GET AWAY WITH IT, RIGHT?

36:14.406 --> 36:17.409
- GIA, IF HE'S GONNA
CLAIM THAT THIS...

36:17.443 --> 36:20.612
RELATIONSHIP
WAS CONSENSUAL,

36:20.646 --> 36:22.281
