40:55.921 --> 40:57.155
SHE'S YOUR NIECE!

40:57.188 --> 40:59.124
WE WERE A FAMILY!

40:59.157 --> 41:01.493
HOW COULD YOU
LET THIS HAPPEN?

41:01.527 --> 41:04.996
[crying]
OH, MY GOD.

41:07.699 --> 41:09.134
OH, MY GOD.

41:09.167 --> 41:13.572
- "ON APRIL 24, 2001."

41:15.206 --> 41:17.509
ON HER 14th BIRTHDAY.

41:17.543 --> 41:22.581
- GIA.

41:22.614 --> 41:25.116
WHAT HAVE I--

41:25.150 --> 41:29.087
OH, MY GOD.

41:29.120 --> 41:34.626
[sobs]

41:36.628 --> 41:38.263
- GEORGE ZANE IS LOOKING
AT MULTIPLE COUNTS

41:38.296 --> 41:41.967
OF SEXUAL ASSAULT
GOING BACK TEN YEARS.

