- IT'S OVER, GIA.
YOU'RE SAFE NOW.

41:48.273 --> 41:53.278
HE'S NEVER GETTING OUT.

41:53.311 --> 41:56.915
HAS YOUR MOM COME
TO SEE YOU YET?

41:56.948 --> 41:58.917
- NO.

41:58.950 --> 42:01.987
AND I DON'T WANT HER TO.

42:02.020 --> 42:03.221
I MEAN, I KNOW I'LL HAVE
TO FORGIVE HER

42:03.254 --> 42:04.322
TO MOVE ON, BUT...

42:04.355 --> 42:07.593
[scoffs]

42:07.626 --> 42:11.897
NOT TODAY.

42:11.930 --> 42:13.999
- YOU SOUND STRONG.

42:14.032 --> 42:18.303
- DR. WHITMERE WARNED ME
IT'S ONLY TEMPORARY.

42:18.336 --> 42:21.172
IT'S GONNA BE
A LONG ROAD BACK.

42:21.206 --> 42:22.908
I'LL PROBABLY
SCREW IT UP.

42:22.941 --> 42:26.578
- NO.
NO, YOU WON'T.

42:26.612 --> 42:30.048
- I KNOW THAT IT'S HARD
TO IMAGINE RIGHT NOW,

42:30.081 --> 42:35.954
BUT YOU SURVIVED
THE ABUSE, GIA.

42:35.987 --> 42:39.224
YOU'RE GONNA SURVIVE
THE RECOVERY.
